RuleName: Check attr for old lookup vs new

Attributes._Description: "In the Q3 2017 release we introduced SER 894, which changed the paper lookups for non-DDPR claims.  This new lookup aligns more closely with the EDI lookup brought in with ESP 2.0 PS2 in Fall/Winter of 2016 (CQ 155423) and Winter/Spring of 2017 (SER 1198).  This switch will allow us to easily go back to the lookup style in Q1 if necessary. - jdm 07/2017"
